0013B2r 2               ; Keyword Table
0013B2r 2               ; ============================================================================
0013B2r 2               ; Format: null-terminated keyword string, then token byte.
0013B2r 2               ; Longer keywords first to prevent partial matches (e.g. GOSUB before GOTO).
0013B2r 2               ; Table terminated by a lone $00.
0013B2r 2               
